ביו ואמר: \"יפה כח הבן מכח האב\".</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://col.org.il/news/2414\">הרב פיקארסקי ל-COL: \"מזה זמן שאני הקרבן\"</a><b> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%95%D7%9F_%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%99%D7%9F\" title=\"חב&quot;ד און ליין\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/15px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/23px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/30px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></b></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://col.org.il/news/2414\">:shmaisהרב פיקרסקי - התפטר מתפקידו</a><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%95%D7%9F_%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%99%D7%9F\" title=\"חב&quot;ד און ליין\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/15px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/23px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/30px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413202255\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.089 seconds\nReal time usage: 1.062 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 219/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4813/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 174/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4072/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.040/7 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5771264/52428800 bytes\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  827.453      1 -total\n 72.36%  598.717      4 תבנית:הערה\n 17.82%  147.463      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים\n  9.74%   80.582      1 תבנית:תורת_הרבי\n  4.84%   40.070      3 תבנית:COL\n  3.76%   31.109      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים/מרחב_שם\n  2.02%   16.676      2 תבנית:שורה_אחת\n  1.29%   10.660      1 תבנית:קח\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:35583-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413202255 and revision id 809989. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"
